  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1227910/extras/ee4d79210e2b74a9f29cb6f3c12785f3.poster.avif?t=1701260797\" width=450 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1227910/extras/ee4d79210e2b74a9f29cb6f3c12785f3.webm?t=1701260797\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1227910/extras/ee4d79210e2b74a9f29cb6f3c12785f3.mp4?t=1701260797\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Roguelite 2</strong> combines roguelike dungeon crawling with turn-based jRPG gameplay.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>-A randomly generated 50-floor dungeon with 15 environments and challenging bosses to conquer<br></li><li>Form a 4-person party with 6  playable classes plus 8 more classes to unlock<br></li><li>Turn-based jRPG-style combat with SNES/yuri-style graphics<br></li><li>Over 200 different treasures to collect, spells to learn and hundreds of enemies to defeat<br></li><li>Random events and weather patterns can cause double monster spawns--or double the treasure!<br></li><li>Over 30 quests to complete to unlock additional classes, gold and starting items<br></li><li>Multiple difficulties for beginners and jRPG veterans<br></li><li>Auto-saving</li></ul>",
